{"tid":1919181,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone SE 2本月底發布及接受訂購，31日舉行盛大活動，屆時將發布iPhone SE 2及其他多款新產品。","createTime":"2020-03-10T15:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T21:31:24.000Z","uid":109923,"like":43,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa99562001aad0b80ca2a0d6274748a453c8da3","tid":1919181,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"新型肺炎疫情持續，暫未有影響蘋果公司較平價iPhone SE 2的發售計劃。公司將於本月底推出新手機，並於同日開始接受訂購。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，蘋果將於本月31日舉行盛大活動，屆時將發布iPhone SE 2及其他多款新產品。iPhone SE 2售價預計為399美元，會於發布當日開始接受訂購。<br />\n<br />\n受疫情影響，蘋果在中國的生產受阻，但iPhone SE 2的交付不會有延誤，因其生產和組裝已轉移至印度等地。<br />\n<br />\niPhone SE 2將採用與iPhone 8相似的外觀，屬4.7英寸屏幕，頂部和底部都保留明顯的邊框，不具備面部識別Face ID功能，採用蘋果自主研發的A13 Bionic晶片。"},{"pid":"c6220e3f55a28452622245d3f80c0d9ef38718ff","tid":1919181,"uid":34213,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"回收夠機殼了"},{"pid":"6ae2a834f735e249cbba444409232cf37609f152","tid":1919181,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"買嚟做後備機 正"},{"pid":"59ab187ce7861ff56dac2d38f3aa2c8cef644137","tid":1919181,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":56,"score":-56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會升級到最新版本ios先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289e3b2186b7fad06eb100e357558d1b1cad2b3c","tid":1919181,"uid":109923,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"59ab187ce7861ff56dac2d38f3aa2c8cef644137","tid":1919181,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":56,"score":-56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會升級到最新版本ios先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"新機點解會冇最新iOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29578c10570d82eca9762079282d9745e55050ca","tid":1919181,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":51,"score":-51,"quote":{"pid":"289e3b2186b7f